                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18060521-1-off1 t18060521-1-cd2"></join>, three blankets, value 14 s. and a sheet, value 1 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18060521-1-victim52" type="victimName">
